      "role": "user",
      "content": "the candles are all burned down now... and there is nothing left but the cold. he is gone, and with him, everything that made this life worth enduring. i feel as though i am already a ghost, just waiting for the heavy velvet of the night to finally claim me and pull me into the silence. it would be so much easier to just... let the darkness take me, wouldn't it?",
